# Node modules and build artifacts inside generated apps
**/results/**/node_modules/
**/results/**/dist/
**/results/**/.vite/
**/results/**/drizzle/

# Telemetry raw logs (large)
**/telemetry/logs.jsonl
**/telemetry/metrics.jsonl
**/telemetry/*.jsonl.bak

# Input snapshots (copies of shared tooling, not source of truth)
**/inputs/

# Playwright
**/playwright/node_modules/
**/playwright/test-results/
**/playwright/playwright-report/
